abstract: Zachary Woolfe reviews performance by New York Philharmonic at Avery Fisher Hall conducted by returning Lorin Maazel.
snippet: After two years away, Lorin Maazel is back for a nine-performance stint at the New York Philharmonic.
lead_paragraph: After two years away, Lorin Maazel is back for a nine-performance stint at the New York Philharmonic.

headline.main: Maazel, a Baton From the Past, Returns for a Visit to the Philharmonic
